
     <div>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>

      <%= link_to "CREATE NEWSLETTER", new_topic_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %><br><br>

      <%= link_to "SUBMIT ISSUE", new_link_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>

      <h3> My Newsletters </h3>
     <% current_user.topics.each do |topic| %>
     <p><%= link_to topic.description, topic_path(topic) %> </p>
     
     <% end %>
           
  <% else %>
     
  <p>Iscoop is an easy way to send animated gifs and other online media to a friend via sms </p>

  <p>Just copy and paste the url of the stuff you want to send, iscoop will automatically embed it for you and you can enter the phone number of your friend add a personal note and click send.</p>

  <p>Your friend will get a text message with the content you send. And its absolutely free</p>     

       
        
  <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
  <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
  <% end %> 
  </div>  

